<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">匯入訂單資料</h1>

  <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded p-6">
    <%= form_with(url: admin_shopline_order_imports_path, method: :post, local: true, class: "space-y-4", multipart: true) do |form| %>
      <div>
        <%= form.label :file, "選擇檔案", class: "block text-gray-700 mb-2" %>
        <%= form.file_field :file, class: "block w-full text-gray-700 border border-gray-300 rounded p-2" %>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">支援的格式：XLS, XLSX, CSV</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6">
        <%= form.submit "開始匯入", class: "bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded" %>
        <%= link_to "取消", admin_shopline_orders_path, class: "ml-2 bg-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-400 text-gray-800 py-2 px-4 rounded" %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">匯入說明</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
      <li>檔案必須包含表頭行作為第一行</li>
      <li>必要欄位：訂單號碼、商品名稱</li>
      <li>請確保電郵欄位資料正確，系統會根據電郵自動關聯客戶資料</li>
      <li>資料中的日期格式應為 YYYY-MM-DD 或 YYYY/MM/DD</li>
      <li>數字欄位請勿加入貨幣符號或千分位逗點</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>